description:
Live Recording - Milano - Friday, September 14th, 2012

Orchestra del Teatro Regio di Torino - Bertrand de Billy, cond.

Andr√© Gallo, piano

I. Andante, Allegro

II. Lento e molto espressivo  09:15

III. Allegro molto  17:55

Sorry, there is a little "gap" in the first mov., because I recorded it from a radio broadcasting... Anyway I hope you will enjoy this less known masterpiece by Debussy played by an amazing young italian pianist and a great friend of mine, Andr√® Gallo.
